lead_paragraph: Yet another rainstorm hit California today, the latest in a weeklong deluge enhanced by El Nino that has forced thousands of people from their homes. By midmorning, scattered showers were reported along the coast from southwestern Oregon to central California.
abstract: Another rainstorm hits California, latest in weeklong deluge enhanced by El Nino that has forced thousands of people from their homes (S)

headline.main: Battered After Days of Storms, California Is Hit by New Rains
